post.description:
Create a StudyFileBundle to associate multiple StudyFiles of dependent types: ```{
  "MM Coordinate Matrix": [
    "10X Genes File",
    "10X Barcodes File"
  ],
  "BAM": [
    "BAM Index"
  ],
  "Cluster": [
    "Coordinate Labels"
  ]
}```

get.description:
Returns all StudyFileBundles for the given Study.  A StudyFileBundle is an object that is used to associate multiple StudyFiles that are only valid when used together:  ```{
  "MM Coordinate Matrix": [
    "10X Genes File",
    "10X Barcodes File"
  ],
  "BAM": [
    "BAM Index"
  ],
  "Cluster": [
    "Coordinate Labels"
  ]
}```
